.TP
\fBcursor down/up\fP 
.br
Seek 1 minute backwards/forwards.

.TP
\fBpage down/up\fP 
.br
Seek 10 minute backwards/forwards.

.TP
\fBspace\fP 
.br
Toggle pause.

.TP
\fBm\fP 
.br
